00:05:37.579 --> 00:05:42.579
the book bearing her name, verse 16 and 17.

00:05:42.579 --> 00:05:45.579
Ruth said,

00:05:45.579 --> 00:05:48.579
Do not plead with me to abandon you,

00:05:48.579 --> 00:05:51.579
to turn back from accompanying you.

00:05:51.579 --> 00:05:54.579
For where you go,

00:05:54.579 --> 00:05:57.579
I will go.

00:05:57.579 --> 00:05:59.579
And where you spend the night,

00:05:59.579 --> 00:06:01.579
I will spend the night.

00:06:01.579 --> 00:06:03.579
Your people will be my people,

00:06:03.579 --> 00:06:06.579
