00:06:12.579 --> 00:06:15.579
May Jehovah do so to me and add to it

00:06:15.579 --> 00:06:17.579
if anything but death

00:06:17.579 --> 00:06:23.060
should separate me from you.

00:06:23.060 --> 00:06:28.370
Now what did all of this actually mean for Ruth?

00:06:28.370 --> 00:06:32.370
It meant leaving what was familiar to her.

00:06:33.370 --> 00:06:39.370
