00:06:46.370 --> 00:06:49.370
or did not even know for that matter.

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:55.370
It meant never returning to what she had left behind.

00:06:55.370 --> 00:06:57.370
When Ruth said to Naomi,

00:06:57.370 --> 00:07:00.370
Where you go, I will go.

00:07:00.370 --> 00:07:02.370
She met with no clauses,

00:07:02.370 --> 00:07:05.370
